text: Filipe Oliveira (born 14 May 1995), also known as Filipe, is a football player who currently plays for Timor-Leste national football team. ==International career== Filipe made his senior international debut against Mongolia national football team in the 2018 FIFA World Cup qualification (AFC) on 12 March 2015.East Timor vs. Mongolia Retrieved 21 August 2017. ==Honours== ===Benfica=== *LFA Super Taça Runner-up: 20162016 Super Taça Liga Futebol AmadoraAS.
